title: Power.Data.Recovery.v4.1.2.Incl.Keygen-ViRiLiTY
description: "Power Data Recovery is a risk-free and READ ONLY data recovery utility." Power Data Recovery is a risk-free and READ ONLY data recovery utility that helps you recover your data after accidental deletion, accidental format, repartition, virus attack, software malfunction, system crash. It is an easy to use data recovery utility that examines your inaccessible hard drives for damages and corruptions and recovers the data back. The supported file systems: FAT 12/16/32 and NTFS. It is easy to use and 4 steps to recover your lost data, no technical knowledge needed. It supports NTFS compressed and encrypted files. It supports Dynamic Volume: Simple Volume, Spanned Volume, Stripe Volume, Mirror Volume,Raid-5 Volume.
